Parks, Trustee for Gulf Transportation Co., v. Judges of the United States District Court for the Eastern District of Louisiana. James E. Ross for petitioner. Eber-hard P. Deutsch and Malcolm W. Monroe for B. F. Leaman & Sons, Inc., in opposition.
